WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
A small bird perches on a branch, already eating from a patch of fungus growing on the wood.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
It takes a bite, then pauses to look around the yard.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Another bird lands on a branch in the background.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
The bird keeps eating, glancing around after each bite.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
A third bird flits onto a nearby branch as the first one continues feeding.